data.description: ***Fully furnished**** Welcome to 25 Wildcat Run, your ultimate cabin retreat nestled in the heart of tranquility. This remarkable property offers an exceptional opportunity for both investors and those seeking an idyllic getaway. Step into this fully remodeled gem and be captivated by its irresistible charm. Every inch of this retreat has been meticulously designed to create an authentic cabin experience. The warm and inviting wood floors throughout the home add a touch of rustic elegance, while the cozy ambiance effortlessly envelops you in a sense of serenity. A highlight of this remarkable property is that it comes fully furnished, making it the perfect turnkey investment opportunity. Whether you plan to generate rental income or simply enjoy your own slice of paradise, this property is ready to welcome you and your guests with open arms. Imagine the convenience of stepping into a fully equipped cabin, where all you need to do is unpack and start making memories. The thoughtfully remodeled interiors showcase exquisite attention to detail. The open-concept layout seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, promoting a sense of togetherness. The kitchen boasts modern appliances, sleek countertops, and ample storage space, allowing you to whip up culinary delights with ease. Gather around the fireplace in the spacious living area and create lasting bonds with loved ones as you share laughter and stories. Escape to the outdoors and indulge in the natural beauty
